India was on 37 for 2 in 4 overs chasing 167 to with the Nidahas Trophy final being played at the Khettarama Stadium, Colombo.Bangladesh totalled 166 for 8 in their allotted 20 overs. Shabbir Rahman was the stand out batsman for Bangladesh making 77 off 50 balls.Mahmudulla made 21.Yuzvendra Chahal mesmerized the Bangladeshi batsmen bagging 3 for 18.